# S08: Living Character & Runner Mode (WOW)

## Objective
Turn the two weakest WOW areas into showpieces:
1. **A living character** — rich emotion set + a ground shadow that behaves physically.
2. **Mode 2 "Note Runner"** — a Chrome-dino-style side-scroller where the **staff scrolls**,
   the avatar runs and hops to help the child hit notes **in time/duration**, playing real
   children's melodies (Twinkle, Mary, Jingle Bells, Happy Birthday, Ode to Joy), speeding up
   only after clean play with a friendly "let's go faster" warning.

Mode 1 (Find) is preserved unchanged — all new behaviour lives in new hooks/screens.

